title: Licence to release non-native wildlife and plants

heading_context: Licence to release non-native wildlife and plants
chunks.html_content:
You must have a licence to grow a plant in the wild or release an animal into the wild if it’s on the list of prohibited species.

Get an application form from Natural England.

heading_context: Licence to release non-native wildlife and plants
chunks.html_content:
To release non-native plants or wildlife contact:

  • NatureScot in Scotland
  • Natural Resources Wales in Wales
  • Department of Agriculture, Environment and Rural Affairs in Northern Ireland
